          <li><b>One etched plate,</b> four chemistries. Color only ever means a verdict.</li>
          <li><b>One typed sentence.</b> The app speaks once, then stops.</li>
          <li><b>The not-yet is dashed.</b> Projected data is never drawn in the solid ink of real history.</li>
        </ul>
